    {
      "id": "q-vue2-vuex",
      "navLabel": "Vuex",
      "question": "Vuex 核心概念有哪些？与组件内 data 如何分工？",
      "questionNote": "Vue 2 项目常考；Vue 3 新项目优先 Pinia，见 Vue 3 章。",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "要点："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Vuex 以单一 state 为中心，mutation 同步改 state，action 处理异步再 commit。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "核心："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "state（单一数据源）、getters（派生状态）、mutations（同步改 state）、actions（异步，再 commit mutation）、modules（分模块）。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "1）组件用 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "mapState"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " / "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "mapActions"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 等辅助函数接入；流程：view dispatch action → commit mutation → state 变 → 视图更新。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "2）放 Vuex：多页面共享的用户/权限/购物车等；放组件：仅本组件 UI 状态。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "3）mutation 必须同步，异步逻辑写在 action；严格模式开发可检测非法直接改 state。"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
