    {
      "id": "q-vue2-computed-watch",
      "navLabel": "computed vs watch",
      "question": "computed 与 watch 有何区别？watch 的 deep / immediate 各起什么作用？",
      "questionNote": "computed 计算派生值且有缓存；watch 执行副作用。不宜用 watch 替代简单计算。",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "要点："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "computed 缓存派生值，watch 执行副作用；不宜用 watch 替代简单计算。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "computed："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "适用于派生状态，"
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "有缓存"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "，依赖不变时不重复计算；可定义 getter/setter。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "watch："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "适用于副作用——发请求、写 localStorage、同步外部系统；可获取新旧值。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "immediate: true"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 使 watch 注册后立即执行一次；"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "deep: true"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 深度监听对象内部，开销更大，宜监听具体字段。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "示例："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "computed 缓存与 watch 副作用的对比。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "computed: {\n  fullName() { return this.first + this.last }\n},\nwatch: {\n  keyword: {\n    immediate: true,\n    handler(v) { this.fetch(v) } // 发请求\n  }\n}"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
